71e0858dc9cf216cd9f07902cc597340b66a3dbf4a25fff8685bfddd87c54ca9c7222ff906fe7bb860a1759f3ce42593a4757a4d8519073d24af401a8501a276  0001-spinner-Add-support-for-wayland-backend.patch
"
